Third Department,

July, 1971

(July 13, 1971) The People of the State of New York ex rel. James Pearson, by Joseph Harris, Petitioner, v. Department of Correction of the State of New York, Respondent.

Application, pursuant to CPLR 7002 (subd. [b], par. 2), for a writ of habeas corpus denied as insufficient on its face (see Code Crim. Pro., §§ 552, 555; People v. Wirtschafter, 305 N. Y. 515, 520-521). Herlihy, P. J., Reynolds, Aulisi, Staley, Jr., and Sweeney, JJ., concur.
